Introduction

Z-Stars was a 13-membered co-ed Z-Pop group. It is a collaborative group of consisting of members from Z-Boys and Z-Girls. They made their debut with the single "Z-Pop Dream" on February 22, 2019, and held their debut stages at the "Z-POP DREAM Live In Seoul" concert on February 23.
